<HEADLINE> Ethiopian Journalists Vow to Fight Against Drug </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ADDIS ABABA, June 27 (Xinhua) -- Ethiopian journalists today
expressed their commitment to the fight against drug abuse and
drug trafficking in the country.
</P>
