Li, who is also minister in charge of State Commission for
Restructuring the Economy, thanked Bottelier for his dedication to
the cooperation between WB and China during his four years as
chief of the WB Resident Mission in China, saying that the
cooperation between the two sides in all fields have developed
smoothly in the past 17 years.
</P>
