social development and economic construction of China.
</P>
<P>
Bottelier said that China's achievements in its reform and
opening-up drive impressed him deeply, expressing that he will
still engage in work related to China after he leaves his present
post and goes back to the WB headquarters next month.
</P>
<P>
Sources from the Chinese Ministry of Finance say that by June
this year, a total of 184 Chinese projects have used WB loans, and
the WB committed loans to China total 28 billion US dollars and of
which, 9.2 billion US dollars are interest-free loans. 
