<HEADLINE> Canadian Firm to Build Fertilizer Plant in Argentina </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BUENOS AIRES, June 27 (Xinhua) -- A multinational company based
in Canada has decided to invest 600 million U.S. dollars in a
nitrogenous fertilizer plant in Argentina.
</P>
