<BODY>
<HEADLINE> Italy Backs Hungary's Efforts to Join NATO: FM </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ROME, June 27 (Xinhua) -- Italy supports Hungary's efforts to
join NATO in the first wave and the European Union as soon as
possible, Italian Foreign Minister Lamberto Dini said here today.
</P>
<P>
Dini made the remarks during talks with his visiting Hungarian
counterpart Kovacs Lazio, who expressed his country's hope to join
the two Western organizations at earliest possible dates.
</P>
<P>
